                    </p>
                  </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="col-md-4">
              <!-- Project 3 goes here -->
              <div class="card text-center">
                <img src="./images/Project3.jpg" class="card-img-top" alt="Project 3 ref image" style="margin-bottom: 3%;">
                <div class="card-body">
                  <h5 class="card-title">Project 3</h5>
                  <p class="card-text">Developed a mobile app for a college that helps the physically challenge to get around campus by being able to use their phones to request for help,
                    have a map of the area and open automatic doors when the phone comes within proximity of a sensor.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
